{"tid":1795774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"家長衰戇鳩搞到安全屋曝光俾黑警知","createTime":"2019-12-24T07:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T07:31:19.000Z","uid":294505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5c8793d10c8a8309646cc57f155ea33334a5376e","tid":1795774,"uid":294505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:14:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母真係好撚嬲，話說依家黑警開始搵到安全屋係因為一啲好戇鳩嘅錯誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說原來有家長一直都係用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">順豐快遞</span></strong>將物資同飯劵寄去安全屋俾小朋友用。<br />\n<br />\n但屌你老母，<ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">順豐</span></span></ins>？（黑人問號）<br />\n<br />\n你地竟然會用間總部喺深圳嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span>（唔係<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span>，係<span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span>）色企業去接觸安全屋。<br />\n<br />\n本世紀最豬隊友非你莫屬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔撚該所有家長、channel admin、金主、甚至住安全屋嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n咪撚再用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">順豐快遞</span></strong>去做任何同安全屋有關嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n又唔係平，派次飯劵要<em>成廿幾蚊</em>，又要<em>冒住俾紅色企業發現嘅風險</em> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵光時聯絡到手足物流去送，同埋用e coupon送飯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a760087f5d59cf7d7ba30c4c9f3f916fd543109","tid":1795774,"uid":138197,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:15:31.000Z","msg":"關撚事咩p牌仔 比人跟呀"},{"pid":"d1ec5b2734a62b3c9b7e01e40add2259015a9e68","tid":1795774,"uid":71480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:31:19.000Z","msg":"Noted"}]}